UPnP Router Control 0.3
***********************

Copyright (C) 2021  Daniele Napolitano <dnax88@gmail.com>

A UPnP router manager for IGD-compliant routers


Compilation and installation
============================

In order to compile UPnP Port Mapper you need following software packages:
    - GTK+ library ( >= 3.10 )
    - GSSDP library
    - GUPnP library
    - cURL library (optional)

To configure run:
	./configure --prefix=/usr

Configure automatically searches for all required components and packages.

If you want to exclude the libcurl dependency and the router icon downloading,
add --disable-libcurl to the configure commnd.

To compile and install run:
	make
	sudo make install


